data.description: Welcome to Foxtrace...NO HOA and NO CITY TAXES! This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is situated on just over a 1/3 acre in a very established subdivision in Hubert. Just a short drive to Camp Lejeune and Swansboro/Emerald Isle, this home offers convenience to both work and play. Enjoy your FOUR bedrooms, along with a great open concept living, dining, and kitchen area. The large backyard is fenced and offers a great patio for grilling and enjoying fall nights. The new Pluris Park is only a couple of houses down and boasts a playground with swing set, playset, and covered pavilions. This beautiful home is ready for new owners today. Schedule your showing!
